•	Advising on planning, building and construction issues to assist with project completion; and
•	Review of project feasibility.

Management Experience
•	Direct staff management and reporting of daily tasks and work flows;
•	Staff performance review and management;
•	Staff recruitment, including interviewing and staff placement;
•	Direct staff coaching and mentoring; and 
•	Direct reporting to partners on issues of fees, billing, client matters, human resources, team matters, business development and marketing.

